==English==

===Noun===
'''Mormon'''  (''plural:'' '''Mormons''')

# A person who belongs to one of the [[Christian]] religous groups related to the religion founded by [[w:Joseph Smith, Jr.|Joseph Smith, Jr.]].  This religion founded by Joseph Smith, is known as The [[church|Church]] of [[Jesus]] [[Christ]] of [[latter|Latter]]-day [[saint|Saints]].
# The ancient American [[prophet]] of Mormon theology who compiled the [[Book of Mormon]].

